around the city.

07:15.500 --> 07:17.667
It's like you're in a movie.
It's awesome.
That sounds fun.

07:17.667 --> 07:19.875
Yeah, it is fun.
You should do it sometime.

07:19.875 --> 07:23.250
I bet it's fun
if you like...

07:23.250 --> 07:25.750
