to a real movie soundtrack

07:25.750 --> 07:27.500
and then it's like
you're in that movie

07:27.500 --> 07:29.959
or your own movie
or whatever.

07:31.333 --> 07:32.708
Yeah.

07:32.708 --> 07:34.250
I'm gonna go, man.

07:34.250 --> 07:35.875
No. Okay.

07:35.875 --> 07:38.417
It's really nice outside,
so you should, uh...

07:38.417 --> 07:41.000
