Yeah, maybe.

07:41.000 --> 07:42.417
I'm not even gonna
put on my jacket.

07:42.417 --> 07:43.458
Don't.

07:43.458 --> 07:45.083
Don't put on your jacket.

07:45.083 --> 07:46.375
