You-- you tell me
how it is, all right?

09:13.834 --> 09:15.583
Okay, Carl.
Okay.

09:26.000 --> 09:27.834
Oh, you're back.
Yeah, I forgot something.

09:27.834 --> 09:28.959
Well, you go right ahead.

09:28.959 --> 09:31.291
No, no, you-- you go.
It's cool.

09:31.291 --> 09:32.792
You sure?
Yeah.

09:32.792 --> 09:35.959
