You're bleeding.

11:36.750 --> 11:38.917
Come use my bathroom.

11:38.917 --> 11:41.750
We'll leave this.
I'll come back for it.
Oh, you're a psychic?

11:41.750 --> 11:44.875
Oh yeah.
I saw that comin'.

11:46.208 --> 11:48.375
What's your name?
Pam.

11:49.333 --> 11:51.500
