are treacherous.

12:04.750 --> 12:07.208
You're lucky
you made it out alive.

12:07.208 --> 12:08.917
Let's see that forehead.

12:12.291 --> 12:15.834
I hope you don't mind
me saying so, Patrick, but...

12:15.834 --> 12:18.125
