(crying continues)

12:34.458 --> 12:35.583
(sniffles)

12:35.583 --> 12:38.834
I'm sorry. Oh, I'm sorry.

12:38.834 --> 12:41.000
It's okay, hon.

12:41.000 --> 12:42.166
I'd offer to give you

12:42.166 --> 12:45.125
